[[div class="email"]]
[[div class="tofrom"]]
**To:** Dr. Jessie Valerie, Junior Team Leader
**From:** Dr. Xavier Fern, Head Researcher
**Subject:** Re:I warned you.
[[/div]]
------
SCiPNet doesn't work that way, and you know that. It’s a highly guarded secret as to how it all works, yeah, but... for God’s sake, a lot of things go into making sure that it’s as up-to-date and secure as possible. Short of being God himself, you can’t get anything into SCiPNet without the proper credentials.

So it’s either the Almighty coming down from the heavens to write this little sisterly fanfiction, or someone with access to the 6535 slot is doing things that you don't know about. Fix this, Valerie.

-Fern
[[/div]]
